elements.text:
After waking up inside
of a slot machine, you
find yourself stuck at 
the starting location. 
You must solve a 
puzzle to continue. An
NPC shows up and 
repeadedly needs 
your help. They 
express their interest 
in you and over time, 
you realize that this 
(Queen of Hearts) has
been intentionally 
making it harder for 
you to escape and 
wants to keep you 
here forever.
elements.originalText: After waking up inside of a slot machine, you find yourself stuck at the starting location. You must solve a puzzle to continue. An NPC shows up and repeadedly needs your help. They express their interest in you and over time, you realize that this (Queen of Hearts) has been intentionally making it harder for you to escape and wants to keep you here forever.
